I've had one lucid dream before, about a week ago. It was about a celebrity being at this house, we were touring it. The celeb left his sweater on the table downstairs so I took it. Eventually my mother and I heard the door bell ring. This guy was touring another home and he said, "Can you watch my kids? I have to go home from this job and the other guys hasn't arrived yet." My mother said no and shut the door. About a minute later the door bell rang again and my mother and I answered it, it was the same guy. He said, "Can you watch them please? There is a shooter around." So my mother went outside and I went too and we looked at the kids, they were at the corner. Out of nowhere this guy wearing black came from behind a bush and had a gun, about to shoot me. I realized I was dreaming and switched it up by making him shoot fire works. It was honestly the dream I could remember. It is extremely hard to achieve lucid dreams but whenever you have them, it's wonder full.
